                     rdfs:label "Data Product Type"@en ;
                     skos:definition "A classification indicating the general kind of Data Product, such as analytical, operational, or reference data."@en ;
                     dp:embedding_note "Data Product Type has definition A classification indicating the general kind of Data Product, such as analytical, operational, or reference data."@en .


